radios.title: Play 99.5
radios.profile_slogan: It's About The Hit Music Station

radio_info.short: Play 99.5 is the Middle East's most vibrant, energetic and original radio station bringing new standards to radio broadcasting in the region. Born on the
radio_info.rest:
5th of October 2004, Play 99.5 was the first privately-owned, commercial English speaking music station, and the first radio station to provide hit music 24 hours a day.

From state of the art studios in the heart of Amman, Play 99.6 broadcasts a mix of the best hits, the coolest live shows, and the competitions and prizes just keep getting bigger and more creative.

Ever since its launch, Play 99.5 has had its fingers on the pulse of its listening community and its betterment.

Play 99.6 has tirelessly put its listeners first from day one and will continue to do so as long as it's on the airwaves.


ADVERTISING

Play 99.5 has actively jumped to the top of the local radio market, with shows and music directly relevant to the lifestyles of our core audience:15 to 30 year olds.

Advertising on Play 99.5 helps clients get their message directly across to their target. Play 99.5 reflects the tastes, attitudes and culture of its audience.

Play 99.6 listeners don't just listen at home and in the car. The station travels everywhere and can be heard in most restaurants, cafes, shops, and offices.
